* 伦理世界秩序Moral World Order (1877);
* 科技进展的伦理与文化意义The Ethical and Cultural Meaning of Technological Progress (1886);
* 伏尔泰Voltaire (1905);
* 电力传输的物理基础On the Physical Foundations of Electric Power Transmission (1905);
* 飞行机器及鸟，飞行技术的历史与批判研究Flight of Machines and Birds. A Historical-Critical Aero Technical In-vestigation (1911);
* 自传Autobiography (1917),
* 战争，军事服务，立法War, Military Service, State Legislation (1921);
* 刑法的哲学Philosophy of Criminal Law (1924);
* 我和社会共识I and Social Conscience (1924);
* 哲学和知识的当然性主要观念On the Main Notions of Philosophy and Certainty of Our Knowledge (1924).

